Class RevisionId

java.lang.Object

java.io.Serializable, IRevisionId
public class RevisionId
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRevisionId

A RevisionId is used to - FIND an AEntity, by the ID or ID and Revision - UPDATE an AEntity by the ID and Revision
